description:
&lt;p&gt;The Short Stay Unit is a 40-bedded, fast paced Unit primarily caring for patients with a length of stay of up to 72 hours. The Short Stay Unit provides care for acute medical patients with a variety of conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Short Stay Unit provides outstanding nursing care and ensures that each patient is discharged in a safe and timely manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer all staff development and training sessions, including a personal development plan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We fully support newly qualified staff through their preceptorship.&lt;/p&gt;
